---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - My Blog" description="Learn more about me and this blog">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <header class="mb-16 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-light text-gray-900 mb-2">About</h1>
      <p class="text-xl font-extralight text-gray-600 leading-normal">
        Get to know me a little better.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="prose prose-lg prose-gray max-w-none">
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Hello! I'm passionate about learning and sharing knowledge. This blog serves as a platform for me to document my journey and hopefully provide value to others along the way.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">What I Write About</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-600">
        <li>Technology and programming insights</li>
        <li>Personal experiences and reflections</li>
        <li>Books I've read and lessons learned</li>
        <li>Travel adventures and discoveries</li>
        <li>Thoughts on productivity and personal growth</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">My Approach</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        I believe in sharing authentic experiences and practical insights. My goal is to create content that's both informative and relatable, helping others learn from my experiences while documenting my own growth.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Get in Touch</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        I'd love to hear from you! Feel free to reach out if you have questions, suggestions, or just want to connect. You can find me on social media or send me an email.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-8 p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Quick Facts</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-1 text-gray-600">
          <li>• Based in the United States</li>
          <li>• Passionate about technology and learning</li>
          <li>• Love reading and exploring new ideas</li>
          <li>• Always curious about the world around me</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout> 